The,Cisco,Flare,API,simplifies,the,deployment,of,a,mobile,device,as,an,interactive,portal,for,accessing,other,devices,and,functional,parameters,within,a,particular,environment,It,is,a,RESTful,API,that,supports,the,use,of,mobile,devices,to,discover,gadgets,and,support,connectivity,to,the,operational,infrastructure,existing,in,a,given,environment,The,API,functionally,designed,to,simultaneously,deploy,a,variety,of,location,technologies,alongside,real,time,communications,capabilities,to,deliver,top,notch,interactive,experiences,for,users